sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Istio as KServe/Istio Gateway<br/>TLS Termination
    participant REST as MLServer REST<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant GRPC as MLServer gRPC<br/>8081/TCP gRPC
    participant Kafka as Kafka Broker<br/>9092/TCP AMQP
    participant MW as Inference Middleware<br/>(CloudEvents)
    participant DP as DataPlane Handler
    participant Cache as Response Cache<br/>(FIFO)
    participant Batch as Adaptive Batcher<br/>(size/time)
    participant Pool as Parallel Pool<br/>(multiprocessing)
    participant Model as MLModel.predict()<br/>(Runtime Plugin)
    participant Metrics as Metrics Server<br/>8082/TCP
    participant OTel as OpenTelemetry Collector<br/>4317/TCP gRPC
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>(PVC/S3)

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 1: REST Inference Request

    Client->>Istio: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>HTTPS (TLS 1.3)
    Istio->>REST: Forward (TLS terminated)<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP
    REST->>MW: Route to handler
    MW->>DP: Process inference request
    DP->>Cache: Check cache (optional)
    alt Cache Hit
        Cache-->>DP: Cached response
    else Cache Miss
        DP->>Batch: Queue request (optional)
        Batch->>Model: Batched predict()
        Model-->>Batch: Batched response
        Batch-->>DP: Individual response
        DP->>Cache: Store in cache
    end
    DP-->>REST: InferenceResponse
    REST-->>Istio: HTTP 200
    Istio-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request

    Client->>Istio: ModelInfer RPC<br/>gRPC/TLS
    Istio->>GRPC: Forward<br/>gRPC 8081/TCP
    GRPC->>DP: Servicer → DataPlane
    DP->>Model: predict()
    Model-->>DP: InferenceResponse
    DP-->>GRPC: Response
    GRPC-->>Istio: gRPC Response
    Istio-->>Client: ModelInferResponse

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 3: Kafka Event-Driven Inference

    Kafka->>REST: Consumer polls topic
    Note right of REST: KafkaServer uses<br/>internal handler
    REST->>DP: Process event
    DP->>Model: predict()
    Model-->>DP: Response
    DP-->>REST: Result
    REST->>Kafka: Producer publishes to output topic

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 4: Parallel Inference (Multi-Worker)

    DP->>Pool: Dispatch request
    Pool->>Pool: Round-robin to worker<br/>(multiprocessing.Queue)
    Pool->>Model: Worker process predict()
    Model-->>Pool: Result via IPC Queue
    Pool-->>DP: Aggregated response

    Note over Client,Storage: Observability

    REST->>OTel: Export traces<br/>OTLP gRPC 4317/TCP (insecure)
    GRPC->>OTel: Export traces<br/>OTLP gRPC 4317/TCP (insecure)
    REST->>Metrics: Starlette metrics
    GRPC->>Metrics: py-grpc-prometheus metrics

    Note over Client,Storage: Model Loading

    Model->>Storage: Load artifacts<br/>/mnt/models (PVC mount)
